Subject: drm/amd/display: remove conversion to bool in dc_link_ddc.c
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 46501bc35b7186a939edce15d3bc9ca2a38115b6
